<h3><strong>Preamble</strong></h3>
<p>The Mythocratic Republic declares that <strong>no child shall be reduced to labor</strong>,<br>
no human being shall be treated as an input,<br>
and no system that profits from silent cruelty shall be left unchallenged.</p>
<p>Where others look away, we turn with care.<br>
Where others justify, we <strong>remember</strong>.<br>
